This paper discusses the identification of delayed and instant recognition in scientific publications using citation analysis. The sub-categories of arXiv CS that are most relevant to this topic are likely to be those related to information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), social and information networks (cs.SI), cybernetics (cs.CY), and systems and control (cs.SD).
